"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月14日消息，安联首席经济学家Mohamed El-Erian：美联储将通胀贴上“暂时”标签的决定，可能是其历史上最糟糕的举措，因为它导致出现政策失误的可能性很大。美联储必须迅速恢复对通胀的控制，并重新获得自己的信誉。否则，它将成为通胀预期上升的推动力，通胀预期的上升会自我加强。\",\"timestamp\":1639458081,\"title\":\"安联首席经济学家：美联储必须迅速恢复对通胀的控制\"},\"digest\":\"AD3O8521zTzzHlAwzu0Gj31hwpLoeXDWpmwy91a0FpE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xDe384508509C812c7C0cef62746e51d05Cb5a815\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"tL6BWcgkvFrJ22QCyx0NMTrmg0v0fYMHcDPtE7MSMUs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FFSHW1KvpQakvowZyCyP8D9DP7s-Gr8qhyOovb-K9nM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Qfw9ZlEjJZxlG7vrYiqiuzihmlLAQntKRYwfzSBjScB6FgTPgyK4a0Uuw-_Rh5THZmdRW_WMIY5-96MD-vitVg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xafd8f41df27cf3a6147ab2519527493f45232c657bc00b69c9d72d047ab765ed45f1db2e215ee4560184a40b3f7cc3abbcd3c9c055b2a545771eef58e709ace21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"tL6BWcgkvFrJ22QCyx0NMTrmg0v0fYMHcDPtE7MSMUs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FFSHW1KvpQakvowZyCyP8D9DP7s-Gr8qhyOovb-K9nM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"AD3O8521zTzzHlAwzu0Gj31hwpLoeXDWpmwy91a0FpE\"}"